special_description = "Bulwark Siegebreaker — swaps the Heavy AP Cannon for a long-range Siege Mortar (AS-tagged, extreme damage vs structures). The siege variant — sit back, lob shells over enemy turret cover. Same chassis durability as base Bulwark."
